name: 0xAuto.io : Contract Auto Deployer
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en: 0xAuto Deployer is a powerful tool designed to expedite token deployment processes. With its exceptional speed and efficiency, it allows users to swiftly create and add liquidity to tokens on various blockchain platforms. The tool enhances transparency, streamlines the deployment process, and empowers creators to capitalize on market trends and opportunities. Its user-friendly interface ensures accessibility for both experienced developers and newcomers. Embrace the future of token deployment with 0xAuto Deployer
